{"tid":610321,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好無助 好攰 可唔可以同我傾下計..","createTime":"2018-03-29T20:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T03:45:22.000Z","uid":54176,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d63009aa68c58652b1071e763f113d7a7610a600","tid":610321,"uid":54176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T20:51:06.000Z","msg":"我係巴<br />\n<br />\n同女朋友拍拖半年 近排多嘈交 嘈交都係一啲大家價值觀上 幾固執既位置<br />\n<br />\n我好愛我女朋友 但係佢每次嘈交都不停講啲悔氣說話 又話不如我搵過個 話想自己一個人走 等等既說話  但我知道佢同埋我都係唔想分手既..<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我其實聽到都會覺得好難受... 我一直都係受氣既一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好愛我女朋友 但係呢段磨合期真係好難捱 我今個星期 冇一日訓到超過三 四個鍾 個心好攰 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下巴絲們 你地當時係點樣捱過磨合期<br />\n我又可以點做好...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝拍緊拖既繼續甜甜蜜蜜 嘈緊交既早日和好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba13c26dbfd905d83e224f0c7b0fc8713ee86c1b","tid":610321,"uid":54176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T21:02:29.000Z","msg":"正負評既巴打 可唔可以傾兩句啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e050ef98f6c17005c89f5449722e5b2ad3acf2","tid":610321,"uid":49091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T21:03:17.000Z","msg":"同你講 頂撚住 <br />\n到你失去咗個下<br />\n你先發現，你真喺好撚愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0d0b3141ff8617e9f2fa0084a22b1a4f0a0b4a","tid":610321,"uid":68389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T21:08:21.000Z","msg":"大家傾多啲計 認真傾果隻 有咩都拎出嚟傾 唔好忍唔住又嘈 忍忍下 就過左<br />\n 最緊要大家知大家都唔想分手 諗下對方對自己做過啲sweet野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50f03cc11fd9c666acd7cbbb1d49e5efe9fb279","tid":610321,"uid":68389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T21:10:43.000Z","msg":"之前一個星期有幾日都考慮緊分手... 但係諗下分手之後嘅日子 就會忍唔住喊 知道自己唔想冇左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n加油呀巴打"},{"pid":"d5d2f9875f6072eaf8383eb2c33abc5994a6542d","tid":610321,"uid":112459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T21:14:37.000Z","msg":"前排都係咁既情況<br />\n每日佢都不停喊<br />\n老實講好煩<br />\n但係將所有野攤出嚟講<br />\n認真(唔需要理性 當然都現實返少少)咁傾返原因<br />\n咁就平安渡過了"},{"pid":"67f4f8c41a5ccfe59dc76ccad936f58fbff09b24","tid":610321,"uid":54176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T21:20:23.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然好攰 但冇諗過放手 <br />\n<br />\n我地都有認真傾過大家既問題 每次傾完都和好返 <br />\n但係近呢幾次 出黎見面傾完之後 當刻係冇事的 仲好返 但隔左一段時間 佢wts返我..都話其實個問題仲放係心入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後無限loop<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知點算好.. 我都係放上黎發下牢騷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#f 多謝你地 我訓一陣先.."},{"pid":"933aa10275ebeb4492f5b52a548c0ce99efe14ab","tid":610321,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T21:21:12.000Z","msg":"分手<br />\n價值觀有好大分別,走下去只會痛苦"},{"pid":"fa0923dc0859d057d459fa572d2face3ef4d995c","tid":610321,"uid":112459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67f4f8c41a5ccfe59dc76ccad936f58fbff09b24","tid":610321,"uid":54176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T21:20:23.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然好攰 但冇諗過放手 <br />\n<br />\n我地都有認真傾過大家既問題 每次傾完都和好返 <br />\n但係近呢幾次 出黎見面傾完之後 當刻係冇事的 仲好返 但隔左一段時間 佢wts返我..都話其實個問題仲放係心入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後無限loop<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知點算好.. 我都係放上黎發下牢騷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #<img src=